showroom.address: Suite 601, Aurora Melbourne Central, 232 Latrobe Street, Melbourne VIC 3000 Australia.

description: The wide, highly visible frontage facing LaTrobe Street and Little LaTrobe Street invites you into the dedicated office lobbies of this mixed-use development, which also includes residences and retail outlets. The lifts bring you up from Level 1 to Level 7 which is occupied by the office podium of this 86-storey building. The office spaces—from strata spaces to single floor plate—are bathed in plenty of natural light, making them conducive for employee well-being and productivity. Options for dining and leisure are available in abundance within the building and in the immediate area. The Melbourne CBD is accessible via the Melbourne Central station, which is only a stone's throw away.
